  <brief_title>A Study of Aleglitazar in Patients With Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus Who Have Not Previously Received Anti-Hyperglycemic Therapy</brief_title>
  <official_title>A MULTICENTER, RANDOMIZED, DOUBLE-BLIND, PLACEBO-CONTROLLED, PHASE III STUDY TO ASSESS THE EFFICACY, SAFETY AND TOLERABILITY OF ALEGLITAZAR MONOTHERAPY COMPARED WITH PLACEBO IN PATIENTS WITH TYPE 2 DIABETES MELLITUS (T2D) WHO ARE DRUG-NA√èVE TO ANTI-HYPERGLYCEMIC THERAPY</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Hoffmann-La Roche</agency>
      <agency_class>Industry</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
